flowchart TD
    A([🔐 LOGIN SCREEN]) --> B{Authenticated?}
    B -- No --> A
    B -- Yes --> C

    C([🏠 DASHBOARD])
    C --> C1[View Status Cards\nActive / Conditional / Deferred]
    C --> C2[PMS Due Alerts]
    C --> C3[Search Plate Number]
    C --> C4[Recent Assessments]
    C --> NAV

    NAV{Bottom Navigation}
    NAV --> C
    NAV --> HIST([📋 HISTORY])
    NAV --> ANA([📊 ANALYTICS])
    NAV --> SET([⚙️ SETTINGS])

    %% NEW ASSESSMENT FLOW
    C -- Start New Assessment --> S1

    S1([STEP 1\n📝 VEHICLE DETAILS])
    S1 --> S1A[Enter Plate Number]
    S1A --> S1B[Enter Technician Name]
    S1B --> S1C[Enter Odometer]
    S1C --> S1D[Select Client]
    S1D --> S1E[Select Branch]
    S1E --> S1F[Select Assessment Type]
    S1F --> S1G{All fields\ncomplete?}
    S1G -- No --> S1A
    S1G -- Yes --> S2

    S2([STEP 2\n🔍 INSPECTION CHECKLIST])
    S2 --> S2A[Engine & Drivetrain\nENG_OIL · ENG_OIL_FILTER · ENG_COOL\nENG_MOUNT · ENG_TRANS · ENG_BELT\nENG_AIR · ENG_FUEL]
    S2A --> S2B[Braking System\nBRK_PAD_F · BRK_PAD_R · BRK_ROTOR\nBRK_FLUID · BRK_HAND · BRK_ABS]
    S2B --> S2C[Suspension & Steering\nSUS_SHOCK · SUS_TIE · SUS_PS · SUS_ALIGN]
    S2C --> S2D[Electrical System\nELC_BATT_V · ELC_BATT · ELC_LIGHTS\nELC_WIPER · ELC_HORN · ELC_DASH]
    S2D --> S2E[Tires & Wheels\nTIR_TREAD_F · TIR_TREAD_R · TIR_PSI\nTIR_SIDE · TIR_SPARE · TIR_NUTS]
    S2E --> S2F[Body & Chassis\nBOD_STRUCT · BOD_UNDER · BOD_DOOR\nBOD_BELT · BOD_WIND]
    S2F --> S2G[LTO Compliance\nLTO_REG · LTO_ORCR · LTO_EMIS\nLTO_MVIS · LTO_INS]

    S2G --> S2H{Each item marked\nPass / Monitor /\nFail / Replaced / NA?}
    S2H -- Not yet --> S2A
    S2H -- All 42 items done --> S3

    %% ITEM RESULT LOGIC
    RESULT_LOGIC([Per-Item Logic])
    RESULT_LOGIC --> RL1[PASS → No action]
    RESULT_LOGIC --> RL2[MONITOR → Note defect\nAdd photo optional]
    RESULT_LOGIC --> RL3[FAIL CRITICAL → Select defect type\nAdd photo + note]
    RESULT_LOGIC --> RL4[REPLACED → Enter part name\nQty · Before+After measure\nPhotos required]
    RESULT_LOGIC --> RL5[N/A → Skip item]

    S3([STEP 3\n🔧 SERVICES & PROCEDURES])

    S3 --> ECU[💻 ECU SCANNING\nMandatory every visit]
    ECU --> ECU1[Add DTC codes or mark No Codes]
    ECU1 --> ECU2[Attach scan report photos]
    ECU2 --> ECU3[Add scan notes]

    S3 --> DEF{Defects found\nin inspection?}
    DEF -- Yes --> DEF1[Mark each defect as Fixed]
    DEF1 --> DEF2[Select action taken\nReplaced / Cleaned / Adjusted etc]
    DEF2 --> DEF3[Enter after-measurement if measurable]
    DEF3 --> DEF4[Add repair note]
    DEF -- No --> TABS

    DEF4 --> TABS

    TABS[Service Tabs]
    TABS --> T1[🗓 PMS — Scheduled\nOil & Filter · Air Filter · Fuel Filter\nBrake Cleaning · Spark Plugs\nBrake Fluid · Coolant · Trans Fluid\nTiming Belt · Diff Oil · Battery]
    TABS --> T2[⚙️ Major Services\nEGR Cleaning · Intake Cleaning\nTurbo Cleaning · ATF Dialysis]
    TABS --> T3[🔍 Troubleshooting\nSensor Cleaning · Replace Parts\nRewire · Reprogram · Other]
    TABS --> T4[📝 Other\nFree-text service description]

    T1 --> DOC[For each checked service\n🔩 Part / Material name\nQty selector\n📷 Up to 5 photos\nBefore · New Part · After]
    T2 --> DOC
    T3 --> DOC
    T4 --> DOC

    DOC --> SUBMIT[Submit Assessment]

    %% RULE ENGINE
    SUBMIT --> ENGINE([⚙️ RULE ENGINE])
    ENGINE --> E1{Any FAIL CRITICAL\nitems remaining?}
    E1 -- Yes → DEFERRED --> E2[Dispatch BLOCKED\nReassessment in 3 days]
    E1 -- No → check monitor --> E3{Any MONITOR\nitems?}
    E3 -- Yes → CONDITIONAL --> E4[Dispatch ALLOWED\nReassessment in 30 days]
    E3 -- No → ACTIVE --> E5[Dispatch ALLOWED\nNo reassessment needed]

    E2 --> RESULT
    E4 --> RESULT
    E5 --> RESULT

    REPLACED_CHECK{All FAIL CRITICAL\nreplaced on-site?}
    ENGINE --> REPLACED_CHECK
    REPLACED_CHECK -- Yes → force ACTIVE --> E5

    %% RESULT SCREEN
    RESULT([📋 RESULT SCREEN])
    RESULT --> R1[Status Banner\nACTIVE / CONDITIONAL / DEFERRED]
    RESULT --> R2[Dispatch Cleared or Blocked]
    RESULT --> R3[Findings Summary\nOpen issues vs Fixed on-site]
    RESULT --> R4[Services Completed\nParts used · Qty · Photos]
    RESULT --> R5[ECU Scan Summary]
    RESULT --> R6[FMS Sync Status]

    RESULT --> ACTIONS{Actions}
    ACTIONS --> ACT1[🏠 Go Home]
    ACTIONS --> ACT2[🚗 Vehicle Profile]
    ACTIONS --> ACT3[📄 Full Report]
    ACTIONS --> ACT4[👤 Supervisor Override]
    ACTIONS --> ACT5[📋 Share Summary\nCopy to clipboard]
    ACTIONS --> ACT6[🔄 Start Re-Assessment]

    %% SUPERVISOR OVERRIDE
    ACT4 --> SUP[Supervisor Panel]
    SUP --> SUP1[Enter supervisor name]
    SUP1 --> SUP2[Add remarks]
    SUP2 --> SUP3[Override reassessment date]
    SUP3 --> SUP4{Clear dispatch\nblock?}
    SUP4 -- Yes --> SUP5[Unit cleared\nStatus → Conditional\nTimestamp recorded]
    SUP4 -- No --> SUP6[Save remarks only]

    %% VEHICLE PROFILE
    ACT2 --> VP([🚗 VEHICLE PROFILE])
    VP --> VP1[Health Score 0-100]
    VP --> VP2[Assessment History tab\nAll past RWAs for plate]
    VP --> VP3[PMS Schedule tab\nNext due km · date · status]
    VP --> VP4[Repeat Defect Warnings\nFlagged 2+ times]
    VP --> VP5[Measurable Value Trends\nBrake pad wear over time]
    VP --> VP6[🔄 Start Re-Assessment]

    %% HISTORY
    HIST --> HF1[Filter by Status\nAll / Active / Conditional / Deferred]
    HF1 --> HF2[Filter by Branch]
    HF2 --> HF3[Search by Plate]
    HF3 --> HF4[Tap any record → Result Screen]

    %% ANALYTICS
    ANA --> AN1[Overview\nFleet-wide status counts]
    AN1 --> AN2[By Branch breakdown]
    AN2 --> AN3[By Client breakdown]
    AN3 --> AN4[Reassessment Queue\nSorted by urgency]
    AN4 --> AN5[Deferred Units list\nOn-hold vehicles]
    AN5 --> AN6[Most Common Defects]

    %% SETTINGS
    SET --> ST1[Mechanic Profile\nName + Branch auto-fill]
    SET --> ST2[App Info & Version]
    SET --> ST3[Branch Coverage stats]
    SET --> ST4[Contact Information]
    SET --> ST5[Reset to Demo Data]
    SET --> ST6[Error Logs\nCopy & clear]
    SET --> ST7[🚪 Log Out]

    %% STYLES
    style A fill:#b91c1c,color:#fff,stroke:#7f1d1d
    style C fill:#b91c1c,color:#fff,stroke:#7f1d1d
    style S1 fill:#1d4ed8,color:#fff,stroke:#1e3a8a
    style S2 fill:#1d4ed8,color:#fff,stroke:#1e3a8a
    style S3 fill:#1d4ed8,color:#fff,stroke:#1e3a8a
    style ENGINE fill:#7c3aed,color:#fff,stroke:#4c1d95
    style RESULT fill:#b91c1c,color:#fff,stroke:#7f1d1d
    style VP fill:#065f46,color:#fff,stroke:#064e3b
    style HIST fill:#92400e,color:#fff,stroke:#78350f
    style ANA fill:#1e3a5f,color:#fff,stroke:#1e3a8a
    style SET fill:#374151,color:#fff,stroke:#111827
    style E2 fill:#dc2626,color:#fff,stroke:#991b1b
    style E4 fill:#d97706,color:#fff,stroke:#92400e
    style E5 fill:#16a34a,color:#fff,stroke:#14532d
    style DOC fill:#0369a1,color:#fff,stroke:#0c4a6e
    style ECU fill:#1d4ed8,color:#fff,stroke:#1e3a8a
